# Field Guide

Field         | Type   | Description
------------- | ------ | ------------
`id`          | Number | The unique identifier reference to the resouce
`username`    | String | The username of the user
`name`        | String | The first name of the user
`sex`         | String | `"male"` or `"female"` or `null`
`avater`      | String | URI of the avatar image of the user

